{"tid":1492630,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家要小心小心小心，中共已經成功令班真心藍絲痴線佬出嚟","createTime":"2019-08-21T02:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T03:27:52.000Z","uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e1aeaec29b34613d39364f68b6953d15109deee","tid":1492630,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:21:13.000Z","msg":"已經有斬人同美國領使館，跟住只會逾嚟逾多，藍絲低智易受影響同時係不受控制<br />\n<br />\n中共想人出嚟愛國但係我唔認為佢地想人係隧道無啦啦斬人，係外國一樣做得好樣衰，佢仲要迫住撐<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係班低智藍絲係痴撚線嘅真心膠，大家一定要小心，佢地真係覺得自己救緊國打緊甲由</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔想同路人再受傷，最理想當然係抆刀就被制服啦，所以一定要小心，甲由論開始有效果"},{"pid":"4add7f8ff0367b1b6945037f9a7054f323ccf17f","tid":1492630,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:21:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1491552/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1491552/page/1</a><br />\n［ 8 2 4 和 你 suck ］行 動 更 新<br />\n建議大家不再分和理非勇武，合力&quot;搞&quot;好香港經濟先可以嬴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMbmerh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMbmerh.jpg&h=ba74c090&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0369fa760130135c7ad9d18f40da63add8662fe2","tid":1492630,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:28:51.000Z","msg":"好多情緒病。"},{"pid":"7056401cfde7bdd574ab5764c30d7fe7538381cf","tid":1492630,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0369fa760130135c7ad9d18f40da63add8662fe2","tid":1492630,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:28:51.000Z","msg":"好多情緒病。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:34:29.000Z","msg":"最慘係藍絲真係唔撚用腦，所以佢先係藍絲，呢樣亦都係最危險，中共應該冇諗過會拖咁耐，攪到而家班真心出嚟派膠，可惜係傷到我地同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9c43e8bd9f375623ba20f2fcba55a894433db6","tid":1492630,"uid":271234,"like"